name: Night and Day wedding ring - 18K gold band and diamonds
description:
Night and day, YOU are the ONE...
Indulge your inner Princess!

A wonderful 18K (18 carats) yellow Gold ring on which I have set many little black and white diamonds.
Wether you want to celebrate a wedding, a commitment, an anniversary or just a little pleasure to spoil yourself (come on, you know you want to), just let me know your ring size and I'll do the rest.

This shank of this band is 5 mm (0.20 inch) wide,
If you need one in rose or white gold no problem, I will make one just for you too. (Price On Application)

One of a kind. The pattern created by the diamonds will never be the same as YOU are truly unique. And if you only want white, or only black diamonds, fancy ones or emeralds, rubies...
Just let me know.

This OOAK jewel will be sent by 1st class, recorded delivery.

name: it's mine Mini dainty skinny 18K yellow gold stacking ring
description:
Made of 18 carat yellow gold, A variation of the MINE rings, skinny, dainty and great enough to wear in stacks of 1 to 100s, although you may have to use several fingers and maybe your toes too?

Simply indicate your finger size in your notes to sellers at checkout, and the little darling will be on its way to you.

This thin simple and elegant ring is 1mm wide. The band is assayed and hallmarked in London Assay Office, which checks the gold quality.
The section of the ring is square. Also available with a round section

to order sizes 4-14 please send us a message or indicate your size in the order

18K gold is a gold alloy made of 75% pure gold, 12.5% sterling silver and 12.5% copper
